173821.「ご…ご高名は かねがね うかがっております。\n 本日は どちらのご丁目を\n:
I have heard of you for many years. Which
street are you looking for today?

173822.「ゴメンゴメン。今のところ\n 新しい家を買う予定は 無いんだー。:
Sorry, sorry. I have no plans to buy a new
house at the moment.

173823.「この島にいる エージェントから\n 君が来ているって聞いて ピンときたんだ。\:
When I heard from my agent here on the island
that you were here, it just clicked. About
where that monster cat is.

173824.「それと 急な頼みで 悪いんだけど\n この先は 君と私\n ふたりっきりで 行:
And I'm sorry to ask on such short notice, but
I'd like you and I to go alone from here on
out.

173825.「……この先では 誰かの不幸な場面を\n 目にするかもしれないからさ。\n あま:
...because down the road you might see someone
in an unfortunate situation. I don't want it
to be too public.

173826.「だから この先は 君だけ一緒に来てほしい。\n 君の準備ができたら 私も行くか:
So from this point forward, I want you to come
with me alone. When you're ready, I'll be
there, so talk to the publicist.

173827.「……これ いつもの所に\n 保管しておいてちょうだい。: Keep this in the usual place.

173832.「わかった。報告ありがとう。: Okay, I understand. Thanks for the report.

173834.「……今回も 世界の均衡は 保たれた。:
Once again, the balance of the world was
maintained.

173835.「今回は いろいろ手伝ってくれて\n 本当 ありがとね。これは 私からの\n 感:
Thank you so much for all your help this time.
This is my way of saying thank you, so please
accept it!

173837.「にゃんだ オマエら。\n まだ 息があったのニャ？ それじゃあ……:
What are you guys doing? You're still
breathing? Well then...

173860.「にゃっふぅ～～～～！！\n 苦しゅうない 苦しゅうない ちこう寄れ！\n 一緒:
Nyahhhh!!! No pain, no pain, come closer!
Let's play together with the cat<heart>

181641.「……かしこまりました。いつもどおり\n リーネ様専用の 地下の大金庫室に\n:
Yes, sir. As usual, we will keep it in the
large vault in the basement for the exclusive
use of Ms. Renee.

181642.「……先ほど レンダーヒルズ\n ８３８８６１丁目の 元住人への入金が\n 完了:
...I just received word that the payment to
the former resident of 838861st Street, Render
Hills, has been completed.

181643.「奪われた財産は 今回の入金で すべて\n 元の所有者に 返却されたとのことです:
All of the property taken was returned to the
original owners with this deposit.

181644.「フフ！ 今後とも アクセサリー合成屋を\n ごひいきにお願いするよ。それと た:
Fufu! I hope you will continue to patronize
Accessory Shop. And maybe I'll even ask you to
be my Bodyguard once in a while.

181645.「ウニャアアアアアアーーーーーッ！！\n オイラが 世界中のおカネを\n 奪って:
Unaaaaaaaaaaaahhh! I'm going to steal all the
money in the world!

181646.「……みんな 不幸で いいワケないでしょ。: There's no reason for everyone to be unhappy.

181647.「そんなチカラを 持ってるんだったら\n 泣いている誰かを 笑わせてみなさいよ\:
If you have that kind of power, try making
someone who is crying laugh, you misunderstood
catoooooo!!

181651.「…………不器用な カミサマだね。: You are a clumsy wife, aren't you?

181653.「なっ……！ アンタ 死んだんじゃないの！？: Hey...! I thought you were dead!

181654.「ボクは ゴールドニャン。\n ヒトに 莫大な富をもたらす ありがた～い\n 神:
I am Gold Cat. I am the god who brings people
great wealth. I offer you this!

181655.「これまで ボクのチカラで 裕福になった人達は\n 財産や 地位や名声を 失うこ:
Until now, those who have become wealthy through my power have only sought after wealth, position, and fame for fear of losing
them.

181656.「アンタしゃんは 見知らぬ誰かを 救うために\n 惜しみなく 自らのゴールドを投:
You gave up your gold to save someone you
didn't even know.

181657.「その イチから 己のチカラで稼いだという\n プライドと信念の宿った 浄財に打:
I was able to return to my old self by being struck by the purity of the money, which I earned from scratch with my own strength and
conviction.

181658.「は……はは。なるほどね。\n 悪霊が 元の善神に 戻ったってワケね。:
Ha...ha. I see. So the evil spirit has
reverted back to the original good god.

181659.「誰かひとりだけ 裕福にするカミサマなんて\n もう ケチくさくて ナンセンスに:
A wife who makes only one person wealthy is
already so stingy and nonsense. I'm going out
of business! Change jobs!

181660.「これからは みんなが幸せになれるよう\n 不幸なヒトに ちょっぴり 手を貸す\:
From now on, I will be a nice and steady wife
who lends a little help to those who are
unhappy so that everyone can be happy.

181661.「さーて これ以上 こんな俗世間にいたら\n 徳が下がるから 元いた場所に 帰る:
Well, if I stay in this mundane world any
longer, I'll lose my virtue, so I'm going back
to where I belong. Bye-bye, Meow!

181662.「まったく 人騒がせな カミサマだね。: You are a very disturbing person, aren't you?

181663.「ハハ……私 こんなんだから\n どこの誰かもわかんない 奴らに\n 命を狙われ:
Haha...because I'm like this, it's not
uncommon for me to have my life threatened by
people from who-knows-what.

181664.「前に 信じられるヒトは\n 数少ない身内だけ……って言ったじゃない？\n あの:
You once told me that the only people you can
trust are the few people in your life. That
was true at the time, but...

181665.「でも ここまで付き合ってくれた\n お人よしな 君のこと……\n 今では 信頼:
But now I'm convinced that I can trust you,
the good-natured guy who went along with me
all this way.

181668.「今度こそ オマエらの\n 息の根を止めにゃいとニャーーーーッ！！: This time, we have to kill them all!

181670.「ダメですニャ～！ いけない お方っ<heart>:
No, no, no! You're not supposed to be
here<heart>

181672.「お～い そこの者よ。マタタビジュースにゃ！\n マタタビジュース 持ってこ～い:
Hey, you there. Get the matatavi juice! Bring
me the matatavi juice!

181674.「黙れ この むっちりスケベ。\n 文字どおり ドロボウ猫のオマエが奪った\n:
Quiet, you pudgy slimeball. You're the definition of a thieving cat... You're going give everyone's treasure back, down to the
last coin!

181675.「フシャーッ！！\n むっちりでも ドロボウ猫でもないニャン！:
Rggghh! I'm not pudgy and I'm not a
thief!!

181676.「オイラ 人間の財産を 根こそぎ奪う\n 最凶の悪霊ニャン！ おそれろニャン！:
I, the deadliest evil spirit that robs humans
of their possessions! Fear me!

181677.「アンタが何者だって カンケーない。\n 私は 理不尽に 人を不幸にする\n ア:
I don't care who you are. I don't care who you
are. I won't let you get away with your
unreasonable misery.

181678.「ニャハッ！ いいことを 教えてやるニャ。\n オイラ もともとは 人々に莫大な:
Nyahaha! I have a good news for you. I used to
be a very wealthy and grateful goddess who
brought great wealth to the people!

181679.「だけど 欲深い奴らが オイラの像をめぐって\n だましあい 裏切りあい 命まで:
But after watching so many greedy people
cheat, betray, and kill each other over a
statue of Ila...

181680.「お金なんかあるから ヒトはおかしくなるニャ！\n あんなモノ ぜーんぶ オイラ:
Money makes people crazy! If I take away all
that stuff, there will be no more conflict in
the human world!

181681.「……そう思ってたら いつの間にか\n ヒトの財産を 根こそぎ奪う\n 悪霊に:
But then, before I knew it, it had turned into
an evil spirit that stole people's property.

181682.「みーんな等しく ビンボーになって\n みーんな等しく 不幸せになれば\n 仲良:
If we all become equally poor, and if we all
become equally unhappy, we will live in
harmony and help each other!

181683.「ニャッ！？\n オマエ さては かなりの 大富豪だニャ？\n おカネのニオイが:
Meow! You must be a Tycoon, huh? I can smell
the money!

181684.「争いを生むだけの おカネなんて\n オイラが 根こそぎ奪ってやるニャ！\n 最:
I'll take all the money you've got that's just
gonna cause trouble! The power of the most
evil spirit.

181685.「私を そんじょそこいらの 小金持ちと\n 一緒にしないでちょうだい。:
Please don't compare me with those little rich
people.

181686.「自分の才能だけで ここまで稼いだ女のチカラ\n とくと 見せてあげるッ！！:
I'll show you the power of a woman who made
this much money on her own talent alone!

181687.「サイッコーに ゴージャスに してあげる！\n うまくいくよう 祈ってなさい！:
I'm gonna make you look absolutely gorgeous!
Fingers crossed!

181688.「アイツの能力は けっこー 厄介だからね。\n リーネさんも 全力を出せるよう\:
His abilities are very annoying. Renee has
changed into her battle suit so that she can
give it her all!

181689.「……にゃんか オマエ すっごく\n イヤな感じがするニャ。: I have a very bad feeling about you.

181690.「オイラのカン かなり 当たるんだニャ。\n だから…………: I have a pretty good instinct. That's why...

181691.「ここで オマエらの息の根を\n 止めておかにゃいとニャァーーーーッ！！: I'm going to have to choke you out right here.

181693.「オラァ！ さっさとしろッ。\n ここはもう オマエらのモンじゃ ねぇんだ！:
Hey! Get on with it. You don't own this place
anymore!

181694.「テメェら さっさと出ていけやッ！: Get the hell out of here!

181696.「あ……あの日……突然 全財産が\n 消えたりしなければ こんなことには……。:
If only... that day... all my money hadn't
suddenly disappeared...

181697.「うっうっ……やだ やだぁ！\n おばあちゃんがくれた ピアノは\n 絶対に 持:
No, no, no, no! I'm taking the piano Grandma
gave me with me, I swear!

181698.「無理を 言わないで……。\n 私たちが これから住む所に\n あんな大きなもの:
Don't be unreasonable... we can't put
something that big where we're going to live.

181699.「ひどい……ひどいよぉ……。\n 大好きだった おばあちゃんの\n のこしてくれ:
It's terrible... terrible... I loved it so
much... It was my grandmother's precious gift
to me...!

188445.「おばあちゃんと たくさん練習した\n 思い出の ピアノなのに……っ！:
It's a piano that I remember practicing with
my grandma a lot...

189499.「……ピアノも ちゃんと取り戻せた？: Did you get the piano back?

189500.「はい 抜かりなく。\n ツバクロ組から 買い戻して\n 例の家族のもとへ 送り:
Yes, not to be outdone. I bought it back from
Tsubakuro's group and sent it off to Your
Family.
